            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَٱلۡفَجۡرِ﴾: أَقْسَم اللهُ بِوَقْتِ الفجْرِ.</h2>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "89:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَلَيَالٍ عَشۡرٖ﴾: هي الليالي العَشْرُ الأُوَلُ مِن ذِي الحِجَّةِ.</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "89:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَٱلشَّفۡعِ﴾: كُلُّ شَيءٍ خَلَقَه اللهُ زَوْجاً فهو شَفْعٌ.</p>\n<h2>﴿وَٱلۡوَتۡرِ﴾: الفَرْدِ.</h2>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "89:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يَسۡرِ﴾: يَسْرِي بِظَلامِهِ.</h2>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "89:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿قَسَمٞ﴾: مَقْنَعٌ ومُكْتَفىً في القَسَمِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿لِذِي حِجۡرٍ﴾: لِصاحِبِ عَقْلٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "89:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "89:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿إِرَمَ﴾: قَبِيلةِ إِرَمَ.</h2>\n<p>﴿ذَاتِ ٱلۡعِمَادِ﴾: صاحبةِ القُوُّةِ والأبْنِيَةِ المَرْفُوعَةِ على الأعْمِدَةِ.</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "89:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿مِثۡلُهَا﴾: مِثْلُ تِلْكَ القَبِيلةِ في الطُّولِ والقُوَّةِ.</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "89:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿جَابُواْ﴾: قَطَعُوا.</h2>\n<p>﴿ٱلصَّخۡرَ﴾: الحَجَرَ العَظِيمَ الصُّلْبَ الَّذِي عَمِلُوا مِنْهُ البُيوتَ.</p>\n<h2>﴿بِٱلۡوَادِ﴾: بِوَادِي القُرَى.</h2>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "89:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ذِي ٱلۡأَوۡتَادِ﴾: صاحِبِ الجُنُودِ الَّذِين ثَبَّتُوا مُلكَهُ، وقَوَّوا لَهُ أَمْرَهُ.</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "89:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿طَغَوۡاْ﴾: تَجَاوَزُوا الحدَّ في الظُّلْمِ.</h2>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "89:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "89:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَصَبَّ عَلَيۡهِمۡ﴾: فَغَشَّاهُم.</h2>\n<h2>﴿سَوۡطَ عَذَابٍ﴾: عَذاباً شَدِيداً.</h2>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "89:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿لَبِٱلۡمِرۡصَادِ﴾: لا يفُوتُه شَيءٌ مِنْ أَعْمالِ العِبادِ.</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "89:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱبۡتَلَىٰهُ﴾: اخْتَبَرَهُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿فَأَكۡرَمَهُۥ﴾: بَسَطَ لَهُ في رِزقِهِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَنَعَّمَهُۥ﴾: جَعَلَه في أَطْيَبِ عَيْشٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "89:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱبۡتَلَىٰهُ﴾: اخْتَبَرَهُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿فَقَدَرَ﴾: فَضَيَّقَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿أَهَٰنَنِ﴾: أَذَلَّنِي بالفَقْرِ.</h2>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "89:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿كَلَّا﴾: ليسَ الأمرُ كَما يَظُنُّ هَذا الإِنْسانُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿لَا تُكۡرِمُونَ﴾: لا تُحْسنُونَ مُعامَلةَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿ٱلۡيَتِيمَ﴾: الطِّفْلَ الَّذِي مَاتَ أبُوهُ وهو صَغِيرٌ.</h2>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "89:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَلَا تَحَٰٓضُّونَ﴾: وَلا يَحثُّ بعضُكُم بعْضاً.</h2>\n<p>﴿ٱلۡمِسۡكِينِ﴾: المُحْتاجِ الَّذِي لا يَمْلِكُ ما يَكْفِيهِ.</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "89:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱلتُّرَاثَ﴾: حُقُوقَ الآخرِينَ في الِميراثِ.</h2>\n<p>﴿لَمّٗا﴾: شَدِيداً، وهو أَن يأكُلَ نَصِيبَهُ وَنَصِيبَ غَيرِه.</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "89:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿جَمّٗا﴾: كَثِيراً مُفْرِطاً.</h2>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "89:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿كَلَّآ﴾: لا ينبغِي أَن يكُونَ حالُكُم كَما ذُكِر.</h2>\n<p>﴿دُكَّتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ﴾: زُلْزِلَتِ الأرْضُ وكَسَّرَ بَعْضُها بَعْضاً.</p>\n<h2>﴿دَكّٗا دَكّٗا﴾: مَرَّةً بعدَ مَرَّةٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "89:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَٱلۡمَلَكُ﴾: والملائِكةُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿صَفّٗا صَفّٗا﴾: صُفُوفاً صُفُوفاً.</h2>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "89:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يَتَذَكَّرُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ﴾: يتَّعِظُ الكافِرُ ويتُوبُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَأَنَّىٰ لَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰ﴾: ومِنْ أينَ لَهُ التَّوبةُ؟</h2>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "89:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿قَدَّمۡتُ﴾: العملَ الصَّالحَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿لِحَيَاتِي﴾: في الآخِرةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "89:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
