            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "89:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَلَا يُوثِقُ﴾: ولا يَشُدُّ ويَربِطُ للعذابِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَثَاقَهُۥٓ﴾: رَبْطَهُ بالسَّلاسِلِ ونَحْوِهَا للعذَابِ.</h2>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "89:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ٱلۡمُطۡمَئِنَّةُ﴾: الموقِنَةُ بِأنَّ اللهَ ربُّها، المطيعةُ لَهُ.</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "89:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿رَاضِيَةٗ﴾: بالثَّوابِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مَرۡضِيَّةٗ﴾: مَرْضِيّاً عَنكِ.</h2>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "89:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فِي عِبَٰدِي﴾: مَعَ عِبادِي، وقيل: في جُمْلةِ عِبادِي الصَّالحِينَ المُطِيعِينَ.</p>"
        },
